<item>
            <title>[JDK-8297036] Generalize C2 stub mechanism</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8297036</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>Currently, we have two implementations of out-of-line stubs in C2, one for safepoint poll stubs (C2SafepointPollStubTable in output.hpp) and another for nmmethod entry barriers (C2EntryBarrierStubTable in output.hpp). I will need a few more for Lilliput: One for checking lock-stack size in method prologue, one for handling lock failures (both for fast-locking), and another one for load-klass slow-path. It would be good to generalize the mechanism and consolidate the existing uses on the new general mechanism.</description>
